<h2 class="section-title">🧠 My Brain</h2>
<p style="color:var(--text-dim);margin-bottom:1rem;text-align:center;">Your neural inventory. Sell back parts you don't want for 80% refund.</p>

<div class="brain-stats glass-card" style="max-width:600px;margin:0 auto 1.5rem;padding:1rem 1.5rem;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;">
  <div><span style="color:var(--text-dim);font-size:0.8rem;">Balance</span><div id="brain-balance" style="font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--accent2);font-family:var(--mono);">$ 10000.00</div></div>
  <div><span style="color:var(--text-dim);font-size:0.8rem;">Inventory Value</span><div id="brain-total" style="font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--cyan);font-family:var(--mono);">$ 0.00</div></div>
</div>

<div id="my-brain-empty" class="glass-card" style="max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.5rem;text-align:center;">
  <p style="font-size:1.2rem;color:var(--text-dim);">🧠 Your brain is empty.</p>
  <p style="color:var(--text-dim);font-size:0.9rem;margin-top:0.5rem;">Browse <a href="/gallery" style="color:var(--accent)">Hardware</a> or <a href="/prebuilts" style="color:var(--accent)">Prebuilts</a> and hit "Sync to Brain" to stock up.</p>
</div>

<div id="my-brain-grid" class="parts-grid" style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;"></div>
